{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/bc_inline_ornament_03.png?t=1723742049\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/bc_caption_02.png?t=1723742049\" /><br>Black Castle is a story-rich dark fantasy adventure that mixes point &amp; click riddles with turn-based puzzles. Solve riddles and explore the castle\u2019s secrets. Master turn-based puzzles to progress through the depths of the castle.<br><br>Deep in the <strong>Black Forest</strong> lies the storied <strong>Black Castle</strong>. A darkness has taken over. Play as Silva, a young student turned adventurer and embark on a quest to rescue your sister Thea.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/Bridge.gif?t=1723742049\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/bc_inline_ornament_03.png?t=1723742049\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/bc_caption_04.png?t=1723742049\" /><br>An ancient bloodline. Dormant powers. A secret calling that must be fulfilled.<br><br>Uncover a world of <strong>medieval horror and witchcraft </strong>with its <strong>ghostly inhabitants</strong>. Unravel the unsettling truth of your heritage. But beware! Dangers await and above all, the terrifying Dark Lord seems to loom. <strong>Will you save your sister and help the castle\u2019s inhabitants along the way?</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/Ghost.gif?t=1723742049\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827710/extras/bc_inline_ornament_03.png?t=1723742049\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"